Bu test fayli. Haqiqiy APK faylni bu yerga joylashtiring.

APK faylni qanday yaratish:

1. Android Studio'da loyihani oching
2. Build > Build Bundle(s) / APK(s) > Build APK(s)
3. Tayyor APK faylni bu papkaga ko'chiring

Yoki Capacitor orqali:
cd frontend
npm run build
npx cap sync android
npx cap open android
# Android Studio'da Build > Build APK

Keyin tayyor APK faylni:
frontend/public/apk/rentcar.apk
ga joylashtiring.
